+## Family Sharing
+
+Family Sharing uses separate relational tables for family spaces, members,
+invitations, and shared goals. Personal app state remains in the user's private
+`app_states` row and is never exposed to family members.
+
+Run the latest [`supabase/schema.sql`](supabase/schema.sql) before testing this
+feature. Invitations are currently in-app: invite the email address the other
+person uses for My Care, then have them sign in and accept it from Family Goals.
+
 ## Local Prototype Backend
 
 An authenticated SQLite REST API is available in [`backend/`](backend/README.md).
